short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Exports your MeTime schedule to Google Calendar at the press of a button

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Exports MeTime schedule to Google Calendar using the Google Calendar API

To export, simply navigate to the roster page and click the new button that says "Save to Google Calendar"

The roster can then be accessed on Google Calendar
